OL,3,CInterest rates held at 5.25% - what is
OL,4,Cthe bank waiting for?
OL,6,FThe Bank of England believes it's
OL,7,Fstill too early to declare victory,
OL,8,FITV News Business and Economics Editor
OL,9,FJoel Hills reports
OL,11,F"The last mile will be the hardest,"
OL,12,Fthe Governor of the Bank of England
OL,13,Fwarned last summer.
OL,15,FThe journey to price-stability since
OL,16,Fthen has proved far less arduous.
