OL,3,CInterest rates held at 5.25% - what is
OL,4,Cthe bank waiting for?
OL,6,FAnnual wage growth and Services Price
OL,7,FInflation both remain above 6% ` a
OL,8,Flevel the Bank is not prepared to
OL,9,Ftolerate.
OL,11,FPut another way: households and
OL,12,Fbusinesses continue to try to reclaim
OL,13,Ftheir lost spending power by
OL,14,Fincreasing their pay and their profits
OL,15,Fin a way the Bank still considers to
OL,16,Fbe inflationary.
