OL,3,CInterest rates held at 5.25% - what is
OL,4,Cthe bank waiting for?
OL,6,FThe Bank's survey of 530 companies,
OL,7,Fwhich employ almost one million
OL,8,Fpeople, suggests the average pay rise
OL,9,Fin April will run at 5.4%. In the
OL,10,FBank's view, that puts upward pressure
OL,11,Fon prices.
OL,13,FWage growth has eased and the Bank
OL,14,Fexpects it to decline further but it
OL,15,Fwants to see proof that's happening.
OL,16,FFor now, interest rates stay where
OL,17,Fthey are.
OL,19,FThe strength of pay growth is not the
OL,20,Fonly worry.
