OL,3,CInterest rates held at 5.25% - what is
OL,4,Cthe bank waiting for?
OL,6,FThe remain a "material risk". The
OL,7,Fprice of shipping freight between Asia
OL,8,Fand Europe has almost quadrupled in
OL,9,Fthe last three months but, for now,
OL,10,Fthe impact on consumer prices in the
OL,11,FUK is judged to be small.
OL,13,FThe Bank's aim here is to keep
OL,14,Fapplying the appropriate amount of
OL,15,Frestraint on demand to bring inflation
OL,16,Funder control while causing the
OL,17,Fminimum amount of distress.
