OL,3,CInterest rates held at 5.25% - what is
OL,4,Cthe bank waiting for?
OL,6,FAnd higher interest rates are causing
OL,7,Fdistress, for many households and
OL,8,Fbusinesses. With 1.6 million mortgages
OL,9,Fset to be repriced this year, monthly
OL,10,Frepayments are set to rise sharply.
OL,12,FToday, the Bank finally opened the
OL,13,Fdoor to interest rate cuts. There are
OL,14,Fplenty people willing it to walk
OL,15,Fthrough.
